high_descs: Move forward a few steps, then towards the left, then forward again to where the dishwasher is.
Pick up the cup that is sitting on the countertop above the dishwasher.
Move over to the left a bit, to the microwave that is on the counter.
Heat up the cup in the microwave before taking it back out and closing the door.
Turn to the right, walk forward a few steps, then turn to the left to face the kitchen sink.
Place the cup down in the kitchen sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated cup in the kitchen sink.

high_descs: Head across the room to the dishwasher
Pick up the golden chalice that is sitting on the counter above the dishwasher
Take a step to the left to stand in front of the microwave
Open the microwave and place the chalice inside to the right of the tomato, then close the door and turn it on. Open the microwave and pick up the chalice the close the door
Turn to the right and go to the sink that is on your left
Place the chalice into the sink in front of the spatula
anns.task_desc: Place a heated chalice into a sink

high_descs: Move to the counter ahead of you, left of the sink.
Pick up the cup on the counter.
Bring the cup to the microwave on the left.
Heat the cup in the microwave.
Bring the heated cup to the sink, right of the microwave.
Put the heated cup in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated cup in the sink.
